claim: The Democratic Republic of the Congo is in South Africa.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The Democratic Republic of the Congo  (  -LSB- ˈkɒŋɡəʊ -RSB- -LSB- kɔ̃ɡo -RSB- ; République démocratique du Congo  )  , also known as DR Congo , DRC , DROC , Congo-Kinshasa or simply the Congo , is a country located in Central Africa .
